targets.query: SHOW TAG VALUES CARDINALITY FROM "vsphere_vsan_performance_host-domclient" WITH KEY = "hostname"  WHERE ("clustername" =~ /^$cluster$/)
SHOW TAG VALUES CARDINALITY FROM "vsphere_vsan_performance_vscsi" WITH KEY = "uuid"  WHERE ("clustername" =~ /^$cluster$/)
SELECT mean("used_latest") * (100 / mean("capacity_latest"))  FROM "vsphere_datastore_disk" WHERE ("source" =~ /^$datastore$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

SELECT (mean("TotalCapacityB") - mean("FreeCapacityB")) / mean("TotalCapacityB") * 100 FROM "vsphere_vsan_summary" WHERE ("clustername" =~ /^$cluster$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SHOW TAG VALUES CARDINALITY FROM "vsphere_vsan_performance_disk-group" WITH KEY = "deviceName"  WHERE ("clustername" =~ /^$cluster$/)
SHOW TAG VALUES CARDINALITY FROM "vsphere_vsan_performance_capacity-disk" WITH KEY = "deviceName"  WHERE ("clustername" =~ /^$cluster$/)
